(1, 'Home line activation', '<p> To require the activation of a home phone line is very simple, you can: </ p> <ul> <li> online request it </ li> <li> to call &nbsp; Customer Service fixed-line &nbsp; 187 </ li > <li> bring to you &nbsp; at a TIM Shop. </ li> </ ul> <p> Check the activation mode by consulting online the various offers available. </ p> <p> the necessary data are: </ p > <ul> <li> name </ li> <li> tax code </ li> <li> home address so request the installation of the line </ li> <li> a mobile telephone number </ li> <li> email address (optional). </ li> </ ul> <p> our technical staff will contact you as soon as possible to arrange an appointment for the telephone system installation. </ p>', '', '<div class="panel-group accordion" id="accordion-15800137">\n\n<div class="panel-default panel">\n\n<div class="panel-heading"> <!-- - Open Div --->\n\n\n<h4 class="blue">\n<a data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#accordion-15800137" href="#collapse-15800137-1" aria-expanded="false" class="collapsed">\nWhat is the removal of a telephone line?\n</a>\n</h4>\n</div> <!-- - Close Div --->\n\n<div id="collapse-15800137-1" class="panel-collapse collapse" aria-expanded="false" style="height: 0px;"> <!-- - Open Div --->\n\n\n<div class="panel-body">\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<p> The move allows you to transfer your telephone line at your new location in the same city or in a different city. </p>\n\n\n\n</div>\n</div> <!-- - Close Div --->\n</div>\n\n<div class="panel-default panel">\n\n\n<div class="panel-heading"> <!-- - Open Div --->\n\n<h4 class="blue">\n<a data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#accordion-15800137" href="#collapse-15800137-2" class="collapsed" aria-expanded="false">\nCan I keep my phone number?\n</a>\n</h4>\n</div> <!-- - Close Div --->\n\n\n<div id="collapse-15800137-2" class="panel-collapse collapse" aria-expanded="false" style="height: 0px;"> <!-- - Open Div --->\n\n<div class="panel-body">\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<p> If the new home is in t