subscription date required to resend the mail <a href="https://areaclienti.mediasetpremium.it/reinvio_conferma_ordine.html"> clicking here. </a> </P > </div> </article> <article> <h3> the content available is the same on different devices? </h3> <div> <p> Yes, the contents are the same for all devices enabled for the service. You can associate up to a maximum of 5 devices, with the vision possible on one device at a time. </P> </div> </article> <article> <h3> Can I see the Mediaset content? </H3> <div> <p> Premium Online offers over the content included in the content of your offer free Mediaset networks (Canale 5, Italy 1 and Rete 4), which are available on-demand as well as live channels, 24 hours 24. complete the offer of free live channels, including Mediaset premium channels such as Iris, Tgcom 24, Top Crime, the 5, 2 and Italian Mediaset Extra. </p> </div> </article> <article> <h3> I do not have a broadband connection, can I subscribe to Premium Online? </h3> <div> <p> to accept the offer TIM Premium Online requires a broadband connection. Call customer service 187 to discover all offers. </P> </div> </article> <article> <h3> What happens if I disable the TIM fixed? </H3 line> <div> <p> The service TIM is a prerequisite to be able to access the offer Premium Online promotional conditions. Therefore, in the event of termination for any cause of TIM Service, the Premium Online Offer will remain active under the conditions of the price list, from time to time, valid for new customers. In the event that the customer has activated the price Premium Online Cinema + Infinity + 2 Events Football PPV (excluding matches UEFA Champions League), will continue to use the service through the list Cinema + Infinity. </P> </div> </article> <article> <h3> What happens in the event of termination or non-activation of the offer TIM? </h3> <div> <p> If you are a customer of TIM SMART HOME / MOBILE FIBRE or no impact on costs TIM of your subscription that will continue to remain a