(13, 'Health and Wellness', 'smartlife', 'TIM', 'Try the latest wearables. Find out how health and wellness can positively change your life. Free your desire to move. Share your results with friends. The future is smart.', '<h2>Samsung Galaxy Gear S with SIM</h2><p>An elegant curved Super AMOLED display for optimal fit, customizable and interchangeable straps screens to better express their own</p>\r\n<h2>Polar Loop H7 HR</h2><p>In conjunction with Polar Heart Rate Sensor. For those who want to measure their business 24 hours a 24 and be driven to achieve daily goals</p>\r\n<h2>Ihealth HS5</h2><p>Record the calories and daily activities, plan weight goals. Organize files, graphics, the historian of the readings and displays trends</p>\r\n<h2>WellUp</h2><p>A free app developed like a personal diary, to arrange at all times of all the information on preventive medical checks periodically for themselves and for the whole family</p>', '<h2>For more informations go to the related devices page and explore all the amazing products that can help you to stay fit!</h2>', 2, 'wearable-health-blog-post1.jpg', 'wearable-health-blog-post1.jpg', NULL, NULL, 0);
